long_description: The Garmin eTrex 10/20/30 carrying case helps protect your GPS from bumps, scuffs and scratches without impeding its usability. Vinyl window and button-friendly design provide a clear view of the screen and easy access to operational buttons. Soft neoprene fabric is reinforced at wear points for added durability. The Garmin eTrex 10/20/30 carrying case features a rip-and-stick closure and open back for use with the GPS's belt clip.
short_description: The Garmin eTrex 10/20/30 carrying case helps protect your GPS from bumps, scuffs and scratches without impeding its usability.
